query.description: Operation response

request.description:
There are a number of things to consider while creating a carrier in Turvo -
  • Creating a carrier requires either a DOT number or an MC number to be specified
  • You can specify a number of payment methods to be associated with a carrier upon creation (and the payment methods need to have been defined in admin console). If the carrier is successfully created, the response will include a Turvo identifier for each payment method specified. You can then define the payment terms in a subsequent PUT request, and use the payment method identifier to associate specific payment methods to a payment term.
